00:27:29.056 --> 00:27:32.966
this presentation in years past. They shared their slides, their

458
00:27:32.976 --> 00:27:36.416
presentations, and their wisdom with me, and that was really helpful.

459
00:27:37.096 --> 00:27:41.036
I'd also like to really thank Marge, Lillian, Alice, Paul,

460
00:27:41.376 --> 00:27:45.136
Lisa, Elena, and all of the AACR staff for the

461
00:27:45.236 --> 00:27:47.496
opportunity to give this presentation.

462
00:27:48.036 --> 00:27:50.416
And also, when I was thinking of the motto

463
00:27:51.296 --> 00:27:55.056
of this meeting, which is Precision, Partnership,

464
00:27:55.216 --> 00:27:55.705
Purpose,

465
00:27:56.736 --> 00:28:00.416
a word that I'd like to add, another P that I'd like to add to

