00:29:32.476 --> 00:29:36.406
possible. And so I know that I'm going back home inspired,

492
00:29:36.536 --> 00:29:40.506
Paul, as you were saying, and excited, and so hopeful, and I

493
00:29:40.556 --> 00:29:43.736
can't wait to see what we do in the years to come as a community.

494
00:29:43.776 --> 00:29:44.756
So thank you very much.

495
00:29:58.056 --> 00:29:59.356
Thank you, Dr. Politi.

