833
00:50:31.384 --> 00:50:34.774
And I think a common question here is what are the emerging

834
00:50:34.834 --> 00:50:37.914
opportunities to meaningfully reduce these longstanding cancer

835
00:50:37.934 --> 00:50:40.934
disparities? And I think a great place to start

836
00:50:41.534 --> 00:50:45.374
is this year's honoree for the AACR Minorities in

837
00:50:45.454 --> 00:50:49.304
