00:52:23.014 --> 00:52:26.284
measure neighborhood features such as access to green space.

864
00:52:26.954 --> 00:52:27.534
Dr. Cheng

865
00:52:28.574 --> 00:52:31.634
talked about her work on developing and disseminating racial and

866
00:52:31.674 --> 00:52:35.294
ethnic-specific measures of structural racism relevant to

867
00:52:35.354 --> 00:52:39.014
cancer. And Dr. Vo Pham presented very

868
00:52:39.054 --> 00:52:41.974
exciting work that she has done to integrate

869
00:52:42.534 --> 00:52:46.084
175 different neighborhood-level

