00:53:46.774 --> 00:53:50.714
this, where we now have the first home assay for cervical cancer

888
00:53:50.794 --> 00:53:54.784
screening, and this will be particularly beneficial for women living in areas with

889
00:53:54.814 --> 00:53:55.934
limited access to

890
00:53:55.954 --> 00:53:59.822
healthcare.And then I also want to

