00:55:13.862 --> 00:55:14.262
impact?

913
00:55:15.502 --> 00:55:17.342
A really great talk was given by Dr.

914
00:55:17.502 --> 00:55:21.052
Wetter, who presented on his common sense framework to

915
00:55:21.162 --> 00:55:24.912
create and sustainably maintain community partnerships with the goal to

