922
00:55:46.202 --> 00:55:49.922
Using this framework, he's had tremendous success across the five-state

923
00:55:50.242 --> 00:55:53.842
Mountain West region that he works in, with over $55

924
00:55:53.862 --> 00:55:57.622
million in funding for programs that are driving risk

925
00:55:57.702 --> 00:56:01.512
factor reductions as well as improving access to cancer screening

926
00:56:01.562 --> 00:56:04.212
across this diverse, largely rural population.

927
00:56:06.322 --> 00:56:08.721
And then the last vignette I'm going to share is this one from Dr.

928
00:56:09.222 --> 00:56:13.162
Baez Conde-Garbanati, who described innovative work that her team

929
00:56:13.202 --> 00:56:16.442
